column5: Charming, large, historic home in West, Texas. Completely renovated to bring back the nostalgic feeling of this incredible town. Surviving the West Explosion, this home sits on the primary street to downtown West. New plumbing, electrical and HVAC gives this home all the luxuries of a modern home but with all the charm of a classic. This gem is within walking distance of all the Czech bakeries and many restaurants and only 14 minutes to Baylor University. Magnolia Market is only 15 minutes away.
